text: Kaye Breadsell (born 2 January 1942) is an Australian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Perth, Western Australia
